testcase.title: To verify NumberOfSites Column is after RecruitmentStatus column in exportTrialResults

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "format = xls and query = cancer and offset = 0 and hits = 100 and expectedValues = exportLiteratureResults1.xls" as parameter to "exportLiteratureResults" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "exportLiteratureResults1.xls"

check for all the columns "Title,Source,Authors,Organisation,Location,Added Date,literatureLanguage,literatureConferenceDetails,Drug Names,Profiles,Thematic Groups,Method Of Action,literatureSummary,literatureExtended,Keywords,Setting,Publication Type" in the file

substeps.message: Number of records in the excel are equal to 100

steps.title: check results number is equal to the "100"
